use the "[36;1m:e[m" (:edit) command:

    [36;1m:e[m <filename>

You can also use the "[36;1m:n[m" (:next) command to load files into Vim:

    [36;1m:n[m <filename(s)>

You can also use the "[36;1m:args[m" command to load files into Vim:

    [36;1m:args[m <filename(s)>

