[1m19.14.[m [36mHow do I make a Vim setting persistent across different Vim[m
       invocations/instances/sessions?

To make a Vim option setting persistent across different Vim instances, add
your setting to the .vimrc or .gvimrc file. You can also use the "[36;1m:mkvimrc[m"
