    [36;1m:help[m 40.1

[1m20.8.[m [36mHow do I create a mapping that works only in normal and operator[m
   pending mode (but not in visual mode)?

Using "[36;1m:map[m" creates a mapping that works in normal, visual+select mode and
operator pending mode. You can use "[36;1m:nmap[m" to have the mapping only work in
normal mode and "[36;1m:vmap[m" to have the mapping only be defined for visual and
